description: Looking at this pic you can tell we all had a ball....or two. It was the best time I've ever had on a boat. Who needs fishing when you have hot papis all around you. I'd rather play with their rods instead. And that's exactly what we did, outside and inside the boat. And if it wasn't for the boats that would pass every once in a while we would have done it in the water and on the JET SKI. Oh well maybe next time...LOL.
title: Dicks Ahoy
